{"tid":1795034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忽發奇想- Holy Water 打怪法","createTime":"2019-12-23T14:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T14:39:55.000Z","uid":319891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4bf44b9854e538ad8592d6087b68dd0823323c","tid":1795034,"uid":319891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">係聖水洗禮呀</div></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地以耶和華之名 為綠色死物淨化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據呢個肉眼掃描 呢D死物永遠都係以綠色皮革包住 唔會收收佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姐係皮革入面好大機會係吸水物 而且死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />物們邪念未夠既好多都係放置式擺放 冇得郁<br />\n <br />\nHoly Water造成既傷害唔洗多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入副本前去道具店買些少聖水彈，上季event有噴射水鐵炮既玩家可以諗下帶唔帶 如果有玩家係混傷魔法師 可以考慮 用埋冰魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n術式使用方法唔洗多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過小心TK呀"},{"pid":"0c8cf28a2b5db9bebe6d0c64faca4973596c95e1","tid":1795034,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［5%捐獻師2.0] 聖誕和你捐challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794786</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUMrN35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUMrN35.jpg&h=34703016&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbtBqQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2